@{
    ViewBag.Title = "BioSite";
}

<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>BioSite</h1>
    <p class="lead">Web application for real-time PCR data calculation.</p>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        Current functionality
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Read Data</h2>
        <p>For now we can use StepOne xlsx file or 1sheep CSV file.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Calculation</h2>
        <p>For now we can calculate Ct, ΔCt and meanCt for each tile and mean + std dev for whole data. Addition, you can recalculate data.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Show data</h2>
        <p>For each tile we can see well name, miRname, ThresholdValue, Ct, ΔCt, meanCt and chart in expanding div where we can inputs for recalculation Ct</p>
        @*<p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301867">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>*@
    </div>
</div>
